OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773497486
OL,3,CMan suspected of offering cocaine to
OL,4,Cracegoers and hiding it under traffic
OL,5,Ccone
OL,7,FA man has been arrested after police
OL,8,Freceived reports of a car driving
OL,9,Faround with a man offering cocaine for
OL,10,Fsale to Ladies' Day racegoers at the
OL,11,FCheltenham Festival.
OL,13,FGloucestershire Police says officers
OL,14,Ffrom the Cheltenham, Gloucester and
OL,15,FCotswolds neighbourhood policing
OL,16,Fteams, dogs unit, special constabulary
OL,17,Fand drone unit worked together to
OL,18,Flocate the car on Wednesday 11 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
