PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773497486
OL,3,CMan suspected of offering cocaine to
OL,4,Cracegoers and hiding it under traffic
OL,5,Ccone
OL,7,FPolice intercepted the car, stopped it
OL,8,Fand searched the vehicle. They said
OL,9,Ffour mobile phones and a large
OL,10,Fquantity of cash were found.
OL,12,FOfficers also found multiple sealed
OL,13,Fpackages of powder hidden underneath a
OL,14,Fnearby traffic cone.
OL,16,FA 33-year-old man from Gloucestershire
OL,17,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fbeing concerned in the supply of Class
OL,19,FA drugs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
